			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '0a2636ae93173421277518cd862dc50c93f1a1b4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/config_values.txt')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/config_values.txt');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('doc/config_values.txt')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/config_values.txt');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') != '66cebfa776e90507aa1cbd0d21265fa82fa761db') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.txt');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/config_values.txt', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/config_values.txt');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') !== '66cebfa776e90507aa1cbd0d21265fa82fa761db') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') !== 'ec531cabd468f87a022f0866ec4458e396f02b87') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/config_values.txt');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/config_values.txt');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/config_values.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/config_values.txt', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.txt') !== '66cebfa776e90507aa1cbd0d21265fa82fa761db') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.txt');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') != 'd878796172ca4a45304d1867c6b8b769da6f4d62') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') !== 'd878796172ca4a45304d1867c6b8b769da6f4d62') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') !== 'c17f5a2d4199bf644719d252f71f8333dea088ee') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio') !== 'd878796172ca4a45304d1867c6b8b769da6f4d62') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.drawio');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png') != '7da531e7c4da6e46c7834f79f0682949a766c03f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png') !== '7da531e7c4da6e46c7834f79f0682949a766c03f') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png') !== '9c63d0f19679956315966b2caf79fe255267e56e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png') !== '7da531e7c4da6e46c7834f79f0682949a766c03f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/class_diagram.png');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: index.php');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('index.php') != '2caa26c002885cfa387801254a8d0e605d8d1bb2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '2caa26c002885cfa387801254a8d0e605d8d1bb2') {
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '75e906ab30b096ca9707d56882d953130029fd99') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== '2caa26c002885cfa387801254a8d0e605d8d1bb2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): index.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.css.php');
	writefile_21();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') != 'ff5d8efc4c6873658fbd3249326b28d1f476d2cc') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.css.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.css.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'ff5d8efc4c6873658fbd3249326b28d1f476d2cc') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== '2c72f363aeffd3d8cc76885ca690b6bd54211a00') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.css.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.css.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.css.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.css.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_21();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'ff5d8efc4c6873658fbd3249326b28d1f476d2cc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.js.php');
	writefile_22();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') != '0d0c535b3d64c451178593532cf233f4f23d7322') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.js.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.js.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '0d0c535b3d64c451178593532cf233f4f23d7322') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== 'aa62a35f20f5798d0c67e3b6b453f2e4e6cde1f9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_22();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '0d0c535b3d64c451178593532cf233f4f23d7322') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') != '89a6aeb41a9d477a627131746d25dc14d3de017a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '89a6aeb41a9d477a627131746d25dc14d3de017a') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '453ee7d9d2fdeec222205da53b350767d318065c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '89a6aeb41a9d477a627131746d25dc14d3de017a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_24();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '2f75482c6022f21a62a5e5486b63b1220252e90f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '2f75482c6022f21a62a5e5486b63b1220252e90f') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '79b1c9b840301ae6f14d6f49975b393d11f80a7d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '2f75482c6022f21a62a5e5486b63b1220252e90f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

			}
		}
		writefile_30();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js') !== 'b8a0ab7a6a4765112972fc85c7e871edcef09126') {

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js');
	writefile_34();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js') != '6e5c3ff53fc7ec35d64295ea1677ef1339d2d583') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js') !== '6e5c3ff53fc7ec35d64295ea1677ef1339d2d583') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js') !== '85bbdeb40da28aebe64e3e1ae61da42db8bacae1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_34();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js') !== '6e5c3ff53fc7ec35d64295ea1677ef1339d2d583') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/092_invite/OIDplusPageRaInvite.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	writefile_35();
	if (!is_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') != '7d4a9a59d38ee7dd100e15be87cd987c0cfeefc3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/includes/setup_base.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== '7d4a9a59d38ee7dd100e15be87cd987c0cfeefc3') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== '98f799954a080e12f27e25bbfae65064d2fe6215') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/includes/setup_base.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/includes/setup_base.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/includes/setup_base.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/includes/setup_base.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_35();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== '7d4a9a59d38ee7dd100e15be87cd987c0cfeefc3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/index.php');
	writefile_36();
	if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/index.php') != 'a155e9a0993c5b2cc06153cff5a89b6a92dc3067') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'a155e9a0993c5b2cc06153cff5a89b6a92dc3067') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '0cf022528360eaca4f97bdbdcfc8028d4ef28700') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

	if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.min.js.php') !== '58eb33d93b8baa58ea3343295e30757244f051ca') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.min.js.php') !== '6e3ed77fcfe17af4f624971e5d31b0ef60839630') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/setup.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/setup.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/setup.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/setup.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_38();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.min.js.php') !== '58eb33d93b8baa58ea3343295e30757244f051ca') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/setup.min.js.php');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('.version.php', "<?php // Revision 702\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('.version.php')) !== '<?php // Revision 702') err('Could not write to .version.php!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
